title: Should we release The Orkan?
body:
Strudel Nation, A proposal has been submitted to implement a series of changes in our protocol. The proposal is called "The Orkan" Read about it here: https://gov.strudel.finance/t/strudel-improvement-proposal-the-orkan/68

Should we implement this proposal?
author: 0x69eF61AFc3AA356e1ac97347119d75cBdAbEF534
